OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776971469
OL,3,CFA Cup semi-final: Southampton fans
OL,4,Curged not to travel to Wembley by train
OL,6,FSouth Western Railway says the work,
OL,7,Fwhich has been planned since 2024,
OL,8,Fmust be completed before the summer to
OL,9,Favoid speed restrictions and reduced
OL,10,Fperformance at one of the busiest
OL,11,Fparts of the SWR network.
OL,13,FMore than 35,000 fans will be heading
OL,14,Fto Wembley for the crucial clash after
OL,15,Fan extra 2,500 tickets were released.
OL,17,FThe train operator said though
OL,18,Fadditional services will run, it won't
OL,19,Fbe enough to cater for all the fans
OL,20,Fhoping to travel on the railway.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776971469
OL,3,CFA Cup semi-final: Southampton fans
OL,4,Curged not to travel to Wembley by train
OL,6,FFor those that are heading to
OL,7,FSouthampton Central, supporters will
OL,8,Fjoin a queuing system to board the
OL,9,Fnext available train.
OL,11,FOther stations including Fareham,
OL,12,FHavant, Clapham Junction and London
OL,13,FWaterloo are expected to be busier
OL,14,Fthan usual.
OL,16,FThere's also a warning that there are
OL,17,Flimited trains returning to
OL,18,FSouthampton after 8pm, which will
OL,19,Faffect supporters' journeys should the
OL,20,Fmatch go to extra time or penalties.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776971469
OL,3,CFA Cup semi-final: Southampton fans
OL,4,Curged not to travel to Wembley by train
OL,6,FStuart Meek, Chief Operating Officer
OL,7,Ffor South Western Railway and Network
OL,8,FRail Wessex, said: "We've been working
OL,9,Fclosely with Southampton Football Club
OL,10,Fsince their quarter-final victory
OL,11,Fearlier this month, and we understand
OL,12,Fjust how much the semi-final means to
OL,13,Fboth their supporters and the City of
OL,14,FSouthampton.
OL,16,F"We have carefully reviewed the work
OL,17,Ftaking place between Woking and
OL,18,FBasingstoke, and because it is safety-
OL,19,Fcritical and must be finished before
OL,20,Fthe summer, it won't be possible to
OL,21,Freschedule.
OL,26,@pD@TOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776971469
OL,3,CFA Cup semi-final: Southampton fans
OL,4,Curged not to travel to Wembley by train
OL,6,F"That's why we must ask supporters to
OL,7,Fconsider alternative travel options
OL,8,Fthis Saturday.
OL,10,F"For those supporters who must travel
OL,11,Fby train, please be aware that there
OL,12,Fwill only be a very limited number of
OL,13,Fservices, and they'll take longer than
OL,14,Fusual.
OL,16,F"Make sure to plan ahead and allow
OL,17,Fextra time to complete your journey.
OL,19,F"We're sorry for the disruption that
OL,20,Fthis weekend's engineering work will
OL,21,Fcause.
OL,26,@rD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776971469
OL,3,CFA Cup semi-final: Southampton fans
OL,4,Curged not to travel to Wembley by train
OL,6,F"We wish Southampton the best of luck
OL,7,Ffor Saturday's game and their attempt
OL,8,Fto repeat the famous run of 1976."
OL,10,FAndy Darbyshire, Head of Event Safety
OL,11,F& Security for Southampton Football
OL,12,FClub, said: "We'd like to say a huge
OL,13,Fthank you to our supporters for the
OL,14,Fincredible backing you're giving the
OL,15,Fteam ahead of this Saturday's FA Cup
OL,16,Fsemifinal.
OL,26,@pD@bO]tD@MOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776971469
OL,3,CFA Cup semi-final: Southampton fans
OL,4,Curged not to travel to Wembley by train
OL,6,F"South Western Railway has advised
OL,7,Fthat train services will be extremely
OL,8,Fbusy, even with additional services in
OL,9,Fplace, and stations are expected to be
OL,10,Fvery crowded with a queuing system at
OL,11,FSouthampton Central.
OL,13,F"Please allow plenty of time for your
OL,14,Fjourney and be prepared that you may
OL,15,Fnot be able to board the first train
OL,16,Fyou intend to take.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776971469
OL,3,CFA Cup semi-final: Southampton fans
OL,4,Curged not to travel to Wembley by train
OL,6,F"A revised timetable will also be in
OL,7,Foperation across parts of the network,
OL,8,Fso we strongly encourage fans to check
OL,9,Ftrain times in advance and listen
OL,10,Fcarefully to station announcements.
OL,12,F"Your support means everything to the
OL,13,Fplayers and staff ` travel safely,
OL,14,Fallow plenty of time, and we look
OL,15,Fforward to seeing the red and white in
OL,16,Ffull voice at Wembley."
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@WO]
